Class InsertRows

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.dragonfly.SqlDirective
      • com.ibm.dragonfly.InsertRows

  • class InsertRows
extends SqlDirective

    This class represents a insertRows directive which inserts sub-templates at bookmarks for each row of the SQL result set.

    Author:
    Mike Storey
